  .notes.handout: :t()
    A \emph{joint action} is an exercise of shared agency.
  .notes: :t()
    Joint actions include very small scale interactions such as hugging or sharing a 
    smile, larger small group efforts like dancing together, going for a walk
    or paining a house, and also epsiodes involving multiple agents and long periods 
    of time like buidling a city or founding a democracy.
  .slide
